353,"uid":309411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f0c33421e902adcb5bbfb2f8c9fa25c517b4164","tid":1512353,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff065e1bbaf756712566400fc6ac44e8bc316d23","tid":1512353,"uid":309411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"你係對自己冇信心定對佢冇信心？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"其實佢都唔會鐘意冇自信的你，你愈係冇自信，愈易呷醋，愈管住佢，愈多鬧交，段關係只會向壞處去發展。<br />\n<br />\n你係驚失去，但你嘅呷醋係唔會減少到佢另揾第二個的機會的。唯一可以做的事，是要增加佢失去你的成本。如果你同佢好地地令佢驚失去你，佢先唔會咁易受其他人誘惑。"},{"pid":"1f57d5ab848bdb1612db81290b33c6185e2ff466","tid":1512353,"uid":238589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275436bae4709ae57bcc4e66fd7cda9331eb10d0","tid":1512353,"uid":234307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:44:53.000Z","msg":"咁撚廢仲學人有女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"4a051647e7c73fb5951d7bc08406e299e033e38e","tid":1512353,"uid":202916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多靚仔獸父吖，肥柒狗公就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw我都想男朋友呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812136309efc4e97d0d8291a1e8ea19fd79af5d","tid":1512353,"uid":309411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a051647e7c73fb5951d7bc08406e299e033e38e","tid":1512353,"uid":202916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多靚仔獸父吖，肥柒狗公就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw我都想男朋友呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"reply